  "text": "We performed the nonparametric Mann-Whitney U test,which does not meet the normality assumption of the one way analysis variance (ANOVA), to evaluate the differences in mean values between two different groups in a similar way to [CITATION_1] . Groups that showed significant difference (p < 0.05) were assigned different letters. Linear regression analysis was also performed to investigate the relationship between GDGT parameters. The statistical testswere performed using the R-3.0.1 package.",
